On URL provided
	render login screen

	User enters username and password.

	If user presses login button
		Store the username, password entered in a global array A
		Render the login screen

	If user pressed View button
		Render the view screen
		pass global array A to an asynchronous mapping function

	asynchronous mapping function
		pass each element of the array A to the iterator function
		which calls the setTimeout() function to print each element
		of the array after a random delay
